data.description: Welcome to 214 West Penn Street.  Located in the heart of Butler, just minutes to local shopping, schools, and area restaurants.  This home welcomes owner & guest with a charming front porch and large entry way.  Nicely sized main level living areas and floor plan.   The second floor features a well sized master bedroom, two additional bedrooms, and two full sized bathrooms.  Be sure to schedule an appointment to see this beautiful Bulter Home.
